<div class="about-page">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <h1>Welcome to TripNest</h1>
    <p>
      We're building a better way to travel — one home, one stay, and one
      experience at a time. With love, from India.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>
      TripNest started as a passion project to connect travelers with unique,
      welcoming places to stay. From apartments in the heart of cities to
      cottages in the hills, our mission is to help people feel at home wherever
      they go.
    </p>
    <p>
      We're more than just a booking platform — we're a bridge between hosts and
      explorers, powered by community and built on trust.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      To empower local hosts and offer guests memorable travel experiences
      through accessible, comfortable, and secure short-term rentals.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Journey So Far</h2>
    <div class="stats-section">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <h3>300+</h3>
