      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <h3>400+</h3>
        <p>Bookings Completed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <h3>40+</h3>
        <p>Trusted Cities</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <h3>100k+</h3>
        <p>Earned by Hosts</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <h2>Built by Passionate Creators</h2>
    <p>
      TripNest is developed and maintained by a team of enthusiastic students
      and professionals who care deeply about technology, design, and making
      travel personal again.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
